    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "12 of 13 V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for model risk level 3. The single below-required factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) reflects the single-condition nature of ASTM F1717 and is accepted by the sponsor based on regulatory adequacy and corroborating clinical evidence. All quantitative acceptance criteria (percent difference <10%, E/uval <1.96) are satisfied for all three QoIs at both laboratories. The package is submitted under ProfileMinimal; digital signature is pending completion of the sponsor signature workflow and will be appended prior to regulatory submission.",
